room_title: Escape room "Curse of the Billy Goat" by King's Escape Room Denver in Denver
room_description: It’s Game 7 of the World Series, and only you know how to break the Curse of the Billy Goat, a curse plaguing your baseball team for over a century. The rival GM found out about your plan and locked you in the home team’s locker room. You must escape and break the curse before the final out. Can you save the team from another century of losing?
